data.description: Assumable 3% FHA mortgage! Get a great home at a great rate. Welcome to this charming, one-story gem in vibrant SE Portland. This delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home exudes a warm and welcoming atmosphere that will capture your heart. Step inside to discover the timeless allure of real hardwood floors that give the space an elegant, cozy feel. With a seamless, single-story layout the home provides the ease of one-story living. The open floor plan and copious natural light from large windows and skylights make the space comfortable year-round. Relax in the spacious, fully-fenced yard with a majestic, mature apple tree. The new deck is the perfect spot to sip your morning coffee or host outdoor gatherings with loved ones. Around the corner from both the stunning Powell Butte Nature Park and a shopping center featuring Fred Meyers, the location balances city convenience with natural beauty. Don't miss your chance to make this charming residence yours. Contact us today and schedule your private tour to experience the warmth and allure of this lovely home in the heart of southeast Portland. Your future begins here!
